<sect2 role="installation">
<title>Installation of TEMPLATE</title>

<para>Install <application>TEMPLATE</application> by running the following 
commands:</para>

<!-- Removed <command> tags. For file creation commands <literal> tags must be added
enclosing the actual text-->
<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

<!--Added the test sute execution-->
<para>To test the results, issue: <command>make check</command>.</para>

<!--Added <systemitem> tag-->
<para>Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:</para>

<!--Changed where the role attribute is placed-->
<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

</sect2>

